{
  "stem": "6944.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And Renia says, look your-- your-- your daughter will be a-- a queen with him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He is a wonderful person.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He is a worker.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He is-- I know him very well because he is the one-- he is the one who helped all his brothers to come out of Poland, and then eventually Palestine.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He made-- he established them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he is just marvelous, and your daughter will be good, will be fine with him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My mother thought, it's-- it's a proposition.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then she said, look, sit down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Write a few words.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Take a photo.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Put it in an envelope.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Give it to Renia, and she will try it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I said, OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Now she says, it's only adventure.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So I said, OK, I will do it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I took a photo, which I have here, and I wrote, 'Dear Mr.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Pelham--' He was Pelham by then.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He was [INAUDIBLE] before, but-- 'Dear Mr.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Pelham, Madame Puter--' In French, by the way-- 'Madame Puterflam has spoken to me about you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "She feels that we should know each other.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "If you are interested, write to me.' Boom, boom.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "That was all I did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And back came a letter, a beautiful letter, saying he's really interested.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He would like to-- to have a-- a little bit more correspondence.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But, as you know, through letters there can't be love.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "There can't be anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So he is proposing that we should write a letter or two, and then maybe something will come out of it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But his letter was so sensible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Now, he says, if I propose to you, I can offer you only three things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "That is a dress, a pair of shoes, and a cinema ticket.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I had to laugh, the honesty of this man!",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Somebody else would promise the world.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
